  "notes": "Live Shopify 2026-04 evidence for LiveHybrid discount effective-catalog reads. The recorder creates an upstream scheduled code discount and scheduled automatic discount, records baseline discount list/count/detail and lone discountNodesCount reads as upstreamCalls, then creates one local-equivalent code discount, updates the upstream automatic discount, deletes the upstream code discount, and captures downstream reads. Proxy replay stages only through public GraphQL mutation/read roots; the upstreamCalls cassette hydrates the real baseline so the list/count/detail targets prove base records survive a staged create, the count-only target proves the shared upstream-count helper adds the staged delta without node hydration, staged updates override hydrated base records, and local tombstones hide upstream code lookup/catalog records."
